modShortDescription: This 7DTD mod adds two Bug-Out Bags that the player recieves upon first entering the game. These bags are filled with clothes, weapons, food and more.
modDescription:
This 7DTD mod adds two Bug-Out Bags that the player recieves upon [first entering](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-starting-items/) the game. These bags are filled with clothes, weapons, first aid kits, food, and other survival type items you may find in a bug-out bag.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/DelStryker/Delmod/tree/master/Delmod_Startup_Packs)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11141-del-stryker-a17-modlet-collection/).

**Credits:** [Del Stryker](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/del-stryker/)
